      • write

        public static void write​(java.io.PrintWriter out,
                         AbstractComponent[] numerics,
                         NumericsExportReport report,
                         NIFBlockingDialog progress,
                         java.lang.String delimiter)
                  throws java.io.IOException,
                         java.lang.InterruptedException
        Writes user defined numerics to the provided file.
        Parameters:
        out - the file writer
        numerics - the components being written to the NIF.
        report - the NIFReport that will show any error messages, etc
        progress - an optional blocking dialog to show progress
        delimiter - the String separating each entry
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs reading the NIF.
        java.lang.InterruptedException

      • convertToNifOutput

        public static java.lang.String convertToNifOutput​(java.lang.String val)
        Transforms the given String to a legal Numeric Import File String.
        Parameters:
        val - the String to transform
        Returns:
        val as a single quote delimited String with an escape character placed before any NIF special purpose characters.

      • sanitize

        public static java.lang.String sanitize​(java.lang.String val)
        Sanitizes a String meant for NIF output. The following transformations are applied:
        • \t becomes \\t
        • \n becomes \\n
        • ' becomes \'
        • , becomes \,
        • \ becomes \\
        • # becomes \#
        Parameters:
        val -
        Returns:
        val with after the transformations were applied
